.pause {
  animation: pulse 30s ease-in-out infinite;
}

/* subtle page fade‑in */
@keyframes fadein {
  from { opacity: 0; }
  to { opacity: 0.96; }
}

/* tiny heartbeat shimmer for the pause marks */
@keyframes pulse {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 0.45; }
  50% { opacity: 0.8; }
}
```

Placed intact, that will make the whole page appear slowly as if the light is coming up, while the little dashes or pause symbols breathe almost imperceptibly.

