  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center;
  text-align: center;
  color: #222;
  animation: heroFade 8s ease-in forwards;
}

@keyframes heroFade {
  from { opacity: 0; }
  to { opacity: 1; }
}
```

Because the bottom of the hero shares the same color as the body background (`#fdfcf8`), the viewer sees a quiet fade instead of an abrupt cut.  
